<div class="faq-question faq-dt-hide-answer faq-processed" data-id="faq1">
<span datatype="" property="dc:title">Do I really need a website?</span>
</div>
<div class="faq-answer faq-dd-hide-answer collapsible faq-processed dhide" id="faq1">
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
<div class="field-items">
<div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded">
<p>When you think that a website is basically a store front that is open 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year, then a website becomes the most viable implementation for your business. By having an online presence customers can view products, services, and other content from your website, from the comfort of their own home whenever they want. By doing this you empower your customers and maximise the marketing potential for future ones. No matter the nature of your business, a website will help your company grow and make money on the web for you.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
